Pra dentro.

17
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,119
Os dois.

18
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,599
Pare.

19
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,759
Entre.

20
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:51,199
